Hey Everyone! 

Bridges international, a student club for international students that partners with Cru, is having an event this Saturday Night! It is a great way to reach out to those with different backgrounds on our campus and reach parts of the world with the Gospel without having to go overseas! Come and enjoy some pizza and make some new friends! We would love to see you there(:
